  "texts": [
    "It seems that a difference of more than two mistakes influenced user ratings of quality.",
    "Taking this into account, it seems necessary to know how well humans and AI detection systems are able to correctly identify humangenerated texts and AI-generated texts that have been created using an obfuscation system.",
    "The results indicated that participants achieved an overall accuracy of 76% in identifying the authorship of texts.",
    "In contrast, AI detection systems did not perform any better than chance, with a bias toward identification of texts as human-generated.",
    "While some scholars have claimed that texts written by ChatGPT and other LLMs are indistinguishable from those written by humans (Susnjak, 2022; Lund et al., 2023), we show this is not entirely true."
  ],
